OL,3,CBody recovered near to Chirk Castle
OL,5,FA body has been recovered in the
OL,6,Fsearch for a missing 17-year-old near
OL,7,FChirk Castle.
OL,9,FA major search took place on Wednesday
OL,10,F8 April with emergency services trying
OL,11,Flocate a teenage boy after reports he
OL,12,Fentered a lake near to the castle on
OL,13,FTuesday.
OL,15,FNorth Wales Police say formal
OL,16,Fidentification has yet to take place
OL,17,Fbut the teenager's family have been
OL,18,Finformed.
OL,20,FThe force says his death is not being
OL,21,Ftreated as suspicious.
