OL,3,CBody recovered near to Chirk Castle
OL,5,FDetective Chief Superintendent Sian
OL,6,FBeck said: "My deepest thoughts and
OL,7,Fcondolences are with his loved ones,
OL,8,Fwho are being supported by specialist
OL,9,Fofficers following this tragic
OL,10,Fincident.
OL,12,F"We kindly ask that the privacy of the
OL,13,Ffamily is respected at this difficult
OL,14,Ftime."
